posting_body: ['Completely updated home in the perfect location!', 'Close to everything!', 'Minutes from Sea-tac Airport, Downtown Seattle or Renton, Tukwila Light Rail Station, Southcenter mall, Boeing field, and all major highways!', 'There is even a bus stop a few steps away!', 'Perfect for commuters.', 'Updated bathrooms and kitchens, freshly painted inside and out.', 'New floors, stainless steel appliances, new windows, and new plumbing and roof.', 'Large-sized deck to enjoy nature.', 'Parking space enough for 4 vehicles.', 'Property management is on-site for any issues or repairs.', 'PROPERTY IS CURRENTLY UNDER CONSTRUCTION', 'The renter is responsible for all utilities.', 'First-month rent and security deposit are due before the start of the lease.', 'The tenant will be required to go through a background and credit check at no cost to the landlord.', 'No smoking allowed.', 'No pets.', 'Landlord will not accept a comprehensive reusable tenant screening report.']
